│ The core logic of the fix remains sound: the VPlan cost model in `precomputeCosts` must be augmented with a fallback mechanism. When an optimized reduction pattern is not found, it     │
│ must cost the individual instructions of the reduction chain (including the PHI node) to match the legacy cost model's behavior and prevent the cost disagreement.                       │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
