│ minimal, correct diff that passes validation.                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The anchor pattern will be the end of the inner `for` loop that checks for reduction patterns. The code to insert is the `if (!FoundPattern)` block that performs the fallback costing.  │
│ I will also inject the `FoundPattern` variable initialization and update as part of this single, comprehensive change.                                                                   │
